move1.name: Bite
move1.description: The target is bitten with viciously sharp fangs. It may make the target flinch.

move2.name: Ember
move2.description: The target is attacked with small flames. It may also leave the target with a burn.

move3.name: Flame Wheel
move3.description: The user cloaks itself in fire and charges at the target. It may also leave the target with a burn.

move4.name: Fire Blast
move4.description: The target is attacked with an intense blast of all-consuming fire. It may also leave the target with a burn.
